{"tid":868600,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 真係多圖 ] 長榮空姐穿 Bikini 拍愛心月曆","createTime":"2018-10-19T15:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T16:44:36.000Z","uid":1221,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"62dba98de9481aa807474e953b1e118e8e1af1b9","tid":868600,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T15:11:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://myblogs.pro/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/448B76B0-F977-40AC-BEA7-885355A27563.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyblogs.pro%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F448B76B0-F977-40AC-BEA7-885355A27563.jpeg&h=78ec4a61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長榮空姐愛心年曆邁入第8年，今年除了有身材高挑美麗的空姐外，首次還有帥哥機師加入拍攝，更首次推出掛曆及桌曆，以比基尼及運動風2種造型呈現，讓帥哥美女們穿著比基尼及運動服拍攝美美的照片，讓你賞心悅目進入2019年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1989659/org/89f286cf12aba0fb67e6a0e236ec0691.jpg/Jyvf77g6eJy2bbmBM9F1qV9vtyAcv5RJo0w0A6NMNAM?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1989659%2Forg%2F89f286cf12aba0fb67e6a0e236ec0691.jpg%2FJyvf77g6eJy2bbmBM9F1qV9vtyAcv5RJo0w0A6NMNAM%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=03785f31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n項目發起人林佳楓表示，今年年曆耗時5個月拍攝、限量6000本，每本年曆售250元台幣（約63港元），當中100元台幣（約25港元）捐贈予兒福聯盟基金會，嚮應公益活動。長榮愛心空姐年曆過去7年已捐贈566萬元（143萬港元）給有關團體，幫助被遺棄或等待被收養的孩子，同時把台灣美麗的風景跟大家分享。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://myblogs.pro/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/BA7F4A01-F25D-4D15-865B-1BCF2C47EC86.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyblogs.pro%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2FBA7F4A01-F25D-4D15-865B-1BCF2C47EC86.jpeg&h=c3521b45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://myblogs.pro/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/41602FDD-BF46-4299-93FF-68A23EFC0E09.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyblogs.pro%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F41602FDD-BF46-4299-93FF-68A23EFC0E09.jpeg&h=f01b1c80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://myblogs.pro/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/D39CFA55-E061-40C7-B84E-EF76C583D004.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyblogs.pro%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2FD39CFA55-E061-40C7-B84E-EF76C583D004.jpeg&h=2fae80b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://myblogs.pro/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/04A19CF4-F0E4-4DF2-A260-27436767884A.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyblogs.pro%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F04A19CF4-F0E4-4DF2-A260-27436767884A.jpeg&h=eb11b4f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://myblogs.pro/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/A91E6B4B-A934-4B48-BBB9-C8DF74CCE550.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyblogs.pro%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2FA91E6B4B-A934-4B48-BBB9-C8DF74CCE550.jpeg&h=4e056566&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://myblogs.pro/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/BD1BCA99-35CE-441D-A257-3005E0317780.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyblogs.pro%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2FBD1BCA99-35CE-441D-A257-3005E0317780.jpeg&h=fd8e3a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://myblogs.pro/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/B71EF18D-5719-4956-A720-BE8377653490.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyblogs.pro%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2FB71EF18D-5719-4956-A720-BE8377653490.jpeg&h=92d23802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://myblogs.pro/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/EE521B60-2198-49AF-ABC7-14B5E060B656.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyblogs.pro%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2FEE521B60-2198-49AF-ABC7-14B5E060B656.jpeg&h=d96b8f38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://myblogs.pro/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/A0631C01-4AFF-42C9-89CF-0CDE47478C30.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyblogs.pro%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2FA0631C01-4AFF-42C9-89CF-0CDE47478C30.jpeg&h=f36a463d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年年曆封面找來前一年的空姐模特兒拍攝，而內頁則由20位新的現職空姐當主角，再加上一位32歲的男機師吳明軒，並結合台灣景色作構圖，與大家分享台灣的美麗。林佳楓指，今年選擇加入男機師拍攝，主要是希望給年輕人一個目標，她透露吳明軒年紀輕輕但相當專業，不僅是長榮航空777的機師，還任職公司教官，當邀請對方拍年曆時，吳明軒也一口答應，十分有愛心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1989660/org/1a0b73abbe4e74a1ab1bf6ebf28d375c.jpg/SmVJM-p3mV1W1v3d8VXkqolqUcZ_XGtOK4ZfDCuGXww?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1989660%2Forg%2F1a0b73abbe4e74a1ab1bf6ebf28d375c.jpg%2FSmVJM-p3mV1W1v3d8VXkqolqUcZ_XGtOK4ZfDCuGXww%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=c84f4054&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://myblogs.pro/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/571F97D6-6D06-4CC6-8E6B-B17B953CB5EF.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyblogs.pro%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F571F97D6-6D06-4CC6-8E6B-B17B953CB5EF.jpeg&h=1f8fe74f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">32歲的男機師吳明軒也是年曆的模特兒之一。</span><br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n多圖在下面"},{"pid":"d40f0019d8c75544ada8fd234861cf00652c8dd8","tid":868600,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T15:11:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1989643/org/b367aa1b87fd8df8ff913fa65ea79aa1.jpg/t5Nips-j71TJ4AIFA7HbT9OFg8e9n12qTkkb0k5JG9I?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1989643%2Forg%2Fb367aa1b87fd8df8ff913fa65ea79aa1.jpg%2Ft5Nips-j71TJ4AIFA7HbT9OFg8e9n12qTkkb0k5JG9I%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=2279e19a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1989650/org/45b08f02ac191a2b81c358cbec24bb6c.jpg/Dxgk-TjqWa-WUx0f-oJNpdp6lva698-N8FIBwvBSAcI?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1989650%2Forg%2F45b08f02ac191a2b81c358cbec24bb6c.jpg%2FDxgk-TjqWa-WUx0f-oJNpdp6lva698-N8FIBwvBSAcI%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=ac5811af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://myblogs.pro/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/A3C94E68-F0B0-4795-9EF3-3E7EEBA33654.jpeg\" da